-- Turkish Airlines Remains Sole Bidder for Polish LOT, Rp.pl Says
-- B y   P i o t r   S k o l i m o w s k i
-- 2012-04-21T08:27:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-21/turkish-airlines-remains-sole-bidder-for-polish-lot-rp-pl-says.html
Turk Hava Yollari AO (THYAO) , known as
Turkish Airlines, is the only prospective bidder for a stake in
 Poland ’s state-owned carrier, Polskie Linie Lotnicze LOT SA,
Rzeczpospolita  reported , citing a Treasury Ministry spokeswoman.  The ministry will pick an adviser for the sale on May 14,
Rzeczpospolita cited Magdalena Kobos as saying. Turkish Airlines
completed a due-diligence process on LOT in March, the newspaper
reported, without saying where it got the information. Kobos
didn’t answer a call to her mobile phone today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Piotr Skolimowski in Warsaw at 
